room_title: Escape room "The Attic" by Escaped In Time in Colorado Springs
room_description:
Your dear old Grandma Esther passed away last month. You've been helping to settle her estate when you stumble upon a hidden room in her attic. Inside, you discover secrets about your “sweet” grandma; secrets that were meant to remain hidden in the attic forever!
You must hurry to unravel these mysteries before your relatives come up and find out what you have discovered and prevent you from becoming the sole heir to an unknown family fortune.
